treat each number LO through HI as an input line
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#shuf-n'\fB\-n, \-\-head\-count=\,COUNT\fP\X'tty: link'\/\fR
output at most COUNT lines
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#shuf-o'\fB\-o, \-\-output=\,FILE\fP\X'tty: link'\/\fR
write result to FILE instead of standard output
.TP
\X'tty: link https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/coreutils.html#shuf--random-source'\fB\-\-random\-source=FILE\fP\X'tty: link'
